{"tid":970941,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣到底係讀銅鑼灣定銅鑼灣？","createTime":"2019-01-06T09:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T03:45:38.000Z","uid":105348,"like":97,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"335afeb79ee26bda5ea1d52e434081a09f886842","tid":970941,"uid":105348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 彎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環"},{"pid":"fe66ccd3ac08048f4fa20723139020de0ac8e431","tid":970941,"uid":119902,"like":2,"dislike":31,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"下，我叫開CWB個喎"},{"pid":"919c0832c1169b38662498d6ebc9b97dd8cbc15d","tid":970941,"uid":51593,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"叫開銅鑼燒"},{"pid":"a25dd12d3df90a24152e09b3c5b75a4d0b385115","tid":970941,"uid":43178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"灣"},{"pid":"32742a912e8c273efb475a9dd7bdbf05efac274a","tid":970941,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"窮後代英文差，叫開銅鑼Bay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5585645a4a408cbdaf65a69ae755a24cebaed8d","tid":970941,"uid":151324,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:48:29.000Z","msg":"叫開大丸"},{"pid":"2750af7022899dba0fb0e9e0a15f7aba0db3e01b","tid":970941,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"32742a912e8c273efb475a9dd7bdbf05efac274a","tid":970941,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"窮後代英文差，叫開銅鑼Bay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"一般念作铜锣湾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13211d27c8cbe7f32c0e49156313d4966b1d01f1","tid":970941,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"咁九龍灣呢？海灣呢？<br />\n唔係照讀海灣個灣咩？"},{"pid":"574f38681f14b721e13881fa45c79f99aab1614d","tid":970941,"uid":82532,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:00:10.000Z","msg":"問:為何香港人會將銅鑼灣、長沙灣讀成銅鑼『環』、長沙『環』呢？<br />\n答: 其實我們可以用聲調來分析一下。灣是陰平聲，環是陽平聲，三字詞的音樂感與兩字詞不同，兩字的如馬(陽上)灣、柴(陽平)灣、深(陰平)灣都不用變讀。長沙「環」(陽平、陰平、陽平)，變讀後更順口，按原來的聲調聽起來是怪怪的。銅鑼「彎」(陽平、陽平、陰平)也有人讀，比長沙「彎」更可接受，不過遠不及銅鑼「環」(陽平、陽平、陽平)多。所以大家便隨讀「銅鑼環」。<br />\n問:為什麼其他「灣」如筲箕灣和淺水灣不用變調?<br />\n答: 因為筲箕灣(陰平、陰平、陰平)和淺水灣(陰上、陰上、陰平)，它們讀「彎」已經順口，所以不用變調。"},{"pid":"6bd28f89c576464c1da8ad460ef53dfae46fb45f","tid":970941,"uid":200834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"我叫開IKEA"},{"pid":"57d1c16b27c34ea1ef476afbc3397d52ccf3c4fb","tid":970941,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"叫開東角"},{"pid":"3a6b90667f050da51dd84a9250417c7b4b8271e5","tid":970941,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57d1c16b27c34ea1ef476afbc3397d52ccf3c4fb","tid":970941,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"叫開東角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:18:57.000Z","msg":"鵝嘴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952077959fbaed0a6ab6544fa43d90221813e37c","tid":970941,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T00:19:24.000Z","msg":"高士威灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bde1df55667153df0aca0ae4190480c076c02c","tid":970941,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:08:12.000Z","msg":"西彎 西環河"},{"pid":"4ed22ba87c2c741557827838948fa7ad1f5cf14e","tid":970941,"uid":77731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:10:10.000Z","msg":"跟地鐵讀<br />\n長沙「環」<br />\n銅鑼「彎」<br />\n土瓜「環」"},{"pid":"a173f10d94fa6c9427a04f05a83805bfd9d13d22","tid":970941,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"高士威灣"},{"pid":"f61a37d01073d7e3244e62a4598ef1017f4f80d8","tid":970941,"uid":159915,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"由細到大不嬲都叫開銅鑼灣 呀爸呀媽都係咁叫 但係大個咗突然聽到有人讀銅鑼灣 都唔知應該叫銅鑼灣定銅鑼灣好 然後上網查過應該係銅鑼灣先啱 所以而家會讀銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d3a046e5c972dbf5adf5745d6c4fe0e4656d32","tid":970941,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"深水灣？淺水灣？清水灣？石排灣？<br />\nOh~銅鑼灣"}]}